Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time,\Nat the far reaches of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,the minor planet\NKumaria exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:49.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The fragments of Kumaria\Nthat remained became
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:53.14,Main,,0,0,0,,a meteor swarm that\Nrained down upon Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,That swarm made the world's\Nbears rise up together as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:00:59.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, they all started\Nattacking humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:02.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, who could've seen\Nthat coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The humans then decided to build\Nthe Wall of Severance in an
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:09.99,Main,,0,0,0,,attempt to drive all the bears,\Nlike us, away from their world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,But guess what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:14.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Silly old man-made rules\Ndon't work on bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Do the math, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,We are bears.\NWe can't help that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:21.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears eat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:23.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That's kind of, like, our thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:25.83,Main,,0,0,0,,And so... Chomp, chomp,\Nmunch, munch...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:29.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NFrom the beginning we hated you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,but also, we loved you from\Nthe beginning, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:36.55,Main,,0,0,0,,All we wanted was to become\Ntrue friends with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:39.18,Main,,0,0,0,,so we had to cross the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,--[LULU] Chomp, chomp.\N--[GINKO] Munch, munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Those bears.\NThey're eating a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:49.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NThose are the transfer students.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,They've transformed, they're\Nonly pretending to be human!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:58.03,Main,,0,0,0,,They're really bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:44.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Tragically, during\Nan attack by two vicious bears,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,our friend, Sumika Izumino\Nlost her earthly life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Next to speak on behalf of the\Nstudent body, Mitsuko Yurizono.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,She has been kind\Nenough to deliver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,--the lovely Sumika's eulogy.\N--[organ plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Sumika Izumino\Nwas a gentle person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.20,Main,,0,0,0,,She regularly showed\Nkindness to the weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,and was always generous\Nwith her love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:12.34,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what, Sumika never\Nlost sight of herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.59,Main,,0,0,0,,bearing the open\Nheart her name sug-- Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:23.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Mitsuko, dear?\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'm sorry,\NI can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Izumino will be remembered\Nlike a white wildflower
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,in the fields of spring.\NShe was brave and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.15,Main,,0,0,0,,She was graceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[gun shots]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NIt can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I refuse to believe my Sumika\Nwas eaten by those awful bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That can't be true! It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Please forgive\NKureha for not being able
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:05.14,Main,,0,0,0,,to come to the memorial today.\NShe's having a difficult time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NPoor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] She's lost someone\Nimportant to her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:19.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine how much\Nshe must be hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:21.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[music box playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Kureha, did you have fun\Nwith your friend again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, please don't look so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, you really love her,\Ndon't you, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll see\Nher another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is just\Nkeep wishing really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:48.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom, it's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NNo matter how hard I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never see Sumika again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I failed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't I\Nprotect my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE STUDENTS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A]\NBears are, like, the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT B] Does the Wall of\NSeverance even do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, if a bear\Ngot through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT C]\NOh, which reminds me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard another girl from\Nthat same class is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A]\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT B]\NYou think the bear got her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT C]\NYeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.88,Main,,0,0,0,,But I guess it can't be official\Nuntil they actually find a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:26.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A]\NBears are disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:27.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Those girls are horrible,\Nbut they still look so tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:34.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You know what's weird.\NThat one girl, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:39.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're right.\NWe can't exactly target her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.57,Main,,0,0,0,,if she refuses to\Nshow up at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki has\Nsuch a delicious smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yummy, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:48.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] He, he, he. When you're\Nbeing cool like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,you have a gorgeous smell, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Like a wild animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:56.04,Main,,0,0,0,,It makes Lulu giddy! [giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:07:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Lulu just had the\Ngreatest idea ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:03.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay, Lulu! So clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NThere's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:14.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro\Nand Lulu Yurigasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Those transfer students\Nare actually bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:22.78,Main,,0,0,0,,But what I saw at the\Nflowerbed is proof I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI]\NMitsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,--Earth to Mitsuko!\N--[MITSUKO] Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, Konomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:33.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You're completely\Nzoned out, Mitsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You've been acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get\Nsuper worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:40.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.92,Main,,0,0,0,,How can you be so concerned\Nabout some random girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI]\NI know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You're trying to\Nget close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What's so great about\NKureha Tsubaki, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:55.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI] Why her? You've gotta\Nknow if you make friends
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:59.56,Main,,0,0,0,,with that girl, the Invisible\NStorm will attack you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to be hurt.\NNow that Sumika's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:06.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha's obviously\Ngoing to be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha will be targeted because\Nshe refused to back down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.74,Main,,0,0,0,,on her love for Sumika.\NGirls who don't follow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,the mood of the herd get\Nexcluded and ostracized.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.67,Main,,0,0,0,,That's how the system\Nworks, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI moans]\NThen why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Because there's\Nmore than Kureha worrying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:24.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI]\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to know by now\Nyou can tell me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,If you say so. The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:34.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw something\Nawful the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[doorbell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey there, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:40.94,Main,,0,0,0,,We're the new transfer students,\Nand you can call this one Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,And my name is Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NMm... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Anyway, we were\Nhoping you'd be a dear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.53,Main,,0,0,0,,and let us stay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,What a cute house!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:54.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not using\Nthe attic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,We'd be fine up there,\Nif that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] What are\Nyou talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw! Ever since Ginko and\NLulu moved to this town
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,we've had to sleep outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! Lulu itches all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:10.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What if it's too late, and she\Nalready has the fleas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:12.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, can't we at\Nleast use your bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.72,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no harm\Nin that, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[squeaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, just\Na bath is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Yay! Negotiation\Nsuccessful! Lulu is clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh! Hold on!\NIt's just for today, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:27.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:28.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you hear me,\Nwhatever your name is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You can call Lulu "Lulu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, and you\Ncan call me Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:43.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I could taste tears on your\Ncheek. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.25,Main,,0,0,0,,You could what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:51.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Bathing, bathing, baths\Nare super-duper fun for Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Bubbles, bubbles everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYou can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but after you finish\Nthat, you both need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NWere you crying? Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Of course\NI wasn't crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Growl. Say what you\Nwill, but I bet you didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,that sad and lonely tears\Ntaste kind of sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NMm... Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl. This is pure heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggles] Lulu can't believe we\Nsafely invaded Kureha's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:35.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's a clever girl?! It's Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so, anyway, once\Nshe's finished in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I want both of you to get out.\NI guess you can still take
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,a bath, though, if\Nyou really want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NI don't. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat's with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.87,Main,,0,0,0,,She won't stop staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:08.63,Main,,0,0,0,,And who in their right\Nmind licks someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Gross. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Not to mention all that\Nweird growl business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:14.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What is that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:17.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Kureha, your\Nlove is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NHuh? Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NI could taste it in your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Your love is a true love.\NGrowl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:26.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NI love you so much, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:39.03,Main,,0,0,0,,And I always will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:43.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] What would\Nyou know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I know because\Nmy love is true, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:50.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA whimpers]\NThere's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have a clue about\NSumika or what she meant to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:54.59,Main,,0,0,0,,So don't pretend like you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:10.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Kureha Tsubaki,\NI've longed to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:17.82,Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, we came here\Nprecisely for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,To see me? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO inahles, exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:24.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Because of your smell.\NSuch a delicious scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! Oh, yes.\NI'll show you my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[doorbell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:39.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWait, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to get away\Nfrom Kureha now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro.\NLulu Yurigasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I know what the two\Nof you really are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,so back offa her, or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I witnessed exactly what\Nyou were doing that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Now get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you\Nlay a finger on Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:16.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Show her what\Nyou really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NGrowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:39.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO growls]\NDamn it, they were too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] I'm sorry,\Nthere's no time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I've gotta go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.92,Main,,0,0,0,,This day can't\Nget any weirder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NUh... Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Is your love\Nthe real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] This is a challenge\Nfrom the Wall of Severance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,If your love is true, go to\Nthe to the roof immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,The bears are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Who is this?\NWhat do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:26.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Give yourself\Nover to the bears,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,and your love will be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,--My love approved?\N--[dial tone]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI]\NMitsuko loves her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:55.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What's so great about that\NKureha girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:58.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her\Nlike this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it. I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:04.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko belongs to me!\NNo one else can have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.74,Main,,0,0,0,,She's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI] Kureha Tsubaki,\Nyou must be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI] I, Konomi Yurikawa,\Nwill eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NKuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI]\NNasty! Nasty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] The time for judgment\Nhas come. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI'll never forgive those bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin them, every one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] What flowers do\Nyou think you'll plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYuri, lilies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NLilies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NThey were my mom's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NWow, they're growing so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It's funny. I've never seen\N'em like this. I always thought
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,lily bulbs were just something\Nyou put in egg custards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Silly Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggles] I sure hope\Nthey bloom soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NNot long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you know your love\Nis about to bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,My love is about to bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYes, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:52.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't back down on\Nmy love! I promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:54.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive the bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin them! Every one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI]\NNas-ss-ss-ss-ss-ss-ss-ss-sty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty girl. Nasty, nasty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I keep missing.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--Die, beast, die!\N--[KONOMI] Nasty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:13.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--Die! Die! Die!\N--Nasty girl! Nasty Girl! Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:14.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NThat thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That monster murdered Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI]\NNasty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NWe want to eat that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,We want to eat her\Nright this minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:45.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NThis court is now in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NWelcome to Severance Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:00.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Let the Yuri Trial begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL]\NYour honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.17,Main,,0,0,0,,They can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,It has been less than a week\Nsince the bears' last kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,We must not allow them to prey\Non any more helpless humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.93,Main,,0,0,0,,This is obvious and\Nblatant overeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Therefore, yes, they are guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What constitutes "mega-hungry"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's subjective and\Ndifferent for every bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NObjection sustained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NBears follow bear instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.44,Main,,0,0,0,,For that is sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant bears, I ask you,\Ndo you want to be invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:39.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Or, would you rather eat humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring on the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NGrowl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] I am now ready\Nto declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:49.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:55.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:19:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NYuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:16.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Growly, growl, growl. growl,\Ngrowl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I Ginko,\Nam going to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] I can't find\Nwhat I'm searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:38.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been searching\Nin the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NSearching for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NSearching for it where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NGive it to me, the Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:02.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI]\NNasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko, where'd you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That was a close\None, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You're okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.64,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I swear there were\Ntwo bears, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.18,Main,,0,0,0,,There must be another\None lurking around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears are usually very\Ncautious, so we should be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:32.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I doubt they'll try\Nto attack again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But still!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[clatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:39.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Kureha, I need\Nyou to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to stop\Nblaming yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Her death isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:46.91,Main,,0,0,0,,The sad truth is, Sumika\Nwas just in the wrong place
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,at the worst possible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:54.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I promise you I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NMitsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think I--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] It's okay\Nto let it out, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You have every right to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.\NYou were her best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Her truest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:12.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[COP A]\NThis is Unit 105.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.87,Main,,0,0,0,,We found a dead bear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,on the Arashigaoka High\NSchool access road.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NSumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:41.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NOh, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:44.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sweet love\Nbelongs to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:48.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Slurp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,That delicious smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:52.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:55.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NAh, you're so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:57.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm aching for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Not yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Tonight is not our night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NGrowl, growl, chomp, chomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, chomp, chomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:15.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, chomp, chomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, chomp, chomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:19.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Still no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:23.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Invisible girls always\Ntaste supremely invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:28.31,Main,,0,0,0,,After tearing apart so many\Nof them, I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Only the excluded ones can be\Ntruly wonderful and delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the girls who refuse\Nto back down on love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:38.53,Main,,0,0,0,,that taste like\Npomegranates and honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:42.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Their meat is the only thing\Nthat will satisfy my hunger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika Izumino, you tasted\Nlike a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.87,0:22:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Soon, the Invisible\NStorm will come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:57.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I want that girl\Nright this minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:03.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.05,0:23:07.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm going to eat you\Nvery soon, growl-growl!
